rows.name: Ask Da Naguth about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066001_SEL1031
rows.name: Ask Da Naguth about the Ganglion.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066001_MSG0001
rows.name: A human? What business have you here?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066001_MSG0002
rows.name: Have you come seeking revenge?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066001_MSG0003
rows.name:
Know that we no longer serve the Ganglion,
and thus have no quarrel with you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066001_MSG0004
rows.name:
But if you insist on a fight, you will get one!
...Well? Why do you not draw your weapon?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066001_MSG0009
rows.name:
We are the Wrothians, human! Our strength is legend!
Our pride is endless![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066001_MSG0010
rows.name:
And impoverished though we may be,
we do not want your aid.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066001_MSG0015
rows.name:
The cold-blooded scoundrels think only of increasing
Samaar's territory. Their members scheme and plot with
no compunction.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066001_MSG0016
rows.name:
And yet we joined them in their wretched acts...
Though circumstances forced our decision,
these sins still weigh heavy on my heart.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066001_MSG0017
rows.name:
I will strike them all down someday,
even if it costs me my life.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066001_MSG0021
rows.name:
If Prince Jiarg has forged an alliance with you,
then it is for us to obey.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066001_MSG0022
rows.name:
My siblings and I are the Three Talons!
Send us against the Ganglion, and we shall annihilate
them like Wrothians possessed![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066001_MSG0023
rows.name:
You will see when the time comes.
No human can fight the way we do.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066001_MSG1001
rows.name:
I saw your battle with that wretched queen jacul,
[ST:playername ]. You fought brilliantly.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066001_MSG1002
rows.name:
In fact, I have never seen a warrior fight with such
ferocity even among my own people.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066001_MSG1003
rows.name:
I am honored to have joined forces with you.
May we meet again on some other battlefield.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066001_MSG1004
rows.name:
Next time, it will be Da Naguth, Cutting Wind of the
Three Talons, who rescues YOU from danger![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066001_MSG1009
rows.name: I thank you for bringing the Ganglion to their end.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066001_MSG1010
rows.name:
But it should have been the Wrothians.
We must atone for the atrocities we inflicted at their
behest upon so many alien races.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066001_MSG1011
rows.name:
I hear many of the Ganglion's forces continue to put up
a fight in Cauldros.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066001_MSG1012
rows.name:
If nothing else, let my fellow Wrothians help you scatter
those fiends to the wind.[ST:wait ]
